{"tid":2400250,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"clubhouse聲網是家中國公司，根據中國國家情報法第七條……","createTime":"2021-02-08T20:40:10.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-11T10:43:55.000Z","uid":261647,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8543314c90509554f635012ccf1faaeeb335f6eb","tid":2400250,"uid":261647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T20:40:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/posts/3686949448041227\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fichentsai.md%2Fposts%2F3686949448041227&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=56809289\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ichentsai.md/posts/3686949448041227</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oQB3onO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoQB3onO.png&h=0f56b815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n作者：蔡依橙的閱讀筆記<br />\n<br />\n聲網是家中國公司，根據中國國家情報法第七條，任何中國公司都必須配合國家情報調查需要，而且必須保密。<br />\n <br />\n「第七条 任何组织和公民都应当依法支持、协助和配合国家情报工作，保守所知悉的国家情报工作秘密。」<br />\n <br />\n所以，如果你還在懷疑聲網會不會把資料提供給中國政府，並用於整肅與國家不同意見者，還想等聲網的公開發言，那這個問題就問錯了，想法也錯了。<br />\n <br />\n因為聲網「一定會」提供中國政府要的資料，不管是錄音檔、轉文字檔、聲紋資訊，都一定會。<br />\n <br />\n而且，你去問聲網的時候，他們「一定會」否認。<br />\n <br />\n- 中华人民共和国国家情报法<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/36UWssi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F36UWssi&d=%2BRZE95FanBIG1LNh2hoNMIHZfmY0V3SDPlGVafywHRI%3D&h=8acbe38e\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/36UWssi</a>"},{"pid":"cef61b78927ede9c97ee1b4424616b0be180e5e0","tid":2400250,"uid":76591,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T22:47:19.000Z","msg":"GFW 已經 Block 咗 Clubhouse 啦"},{"pid":"b87b6a438143a506f2bd3464edaa590101a3c728","tid":2400250,"uid":11809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T00:19:04.000Z","msg":"儍仔先用<br />\n<br />\n冇監控我切"},{"pid":"9761546d1619f3d54b159ab137ed518c0562a3d8","tid":2400250,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T00:21:08.000Z","msg":"唔用最好最保障"},{"pid":"db18c9d861243d2aa96c91d07f2a6317c6d10f71","tid":2400250,"uid":321002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T00:50:57.000Z","msg":"全世界都被強國監控緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12464e565de78038d2126145f192c17433364c33","tid":2400250,"uid":296931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:41:36.000Z","msg":"【認真正視聽】近期假安心app同Clubhouse安唔安裝大論戰嘅盲點<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2403850\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2403850</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e28e0e068365fe7bb9001bd5fc0afde7212ca7f2","tid":2400250,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"見日本呢排都好多人開黎玩<br />\n希望有日本戰線手足傳開去"}]}